Package com.god.kahit.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IEvent
    responsibility: This class is responsible for the events in the application since all events implements this class to be able to be sent on the event bus.
    IEventBus
    responsibility: This class is responsible for posting events for the listeners.
    IItemDataLoader
    Interface used to abstract the implementation of the persistent storage of items used by: ItemDataLoaderRealtime, ItemFactory
    IQuestionDataLoader
    Interface used to abstract the implementation of the persistent storage of questions used by: QuestionDataLoaderRealtime, QuestionFactory

    Debuff  
    Item
    responsibility: This class is responsible for all items which can be bought by players.

    Store

    Team

    VanityItem

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Category
    Enum that represents the different categories that a questions can have, each enum values has a to string method that returns a correct string representation of the values than can be used when loading resources such as values form a database or images and an getId method that returns a unique id that is used in network communication.
    GameMode
    responsibility: This class is responsible for declaring which game mode a player is currently in.
